  "text": "• MRI of (at least the cervical) spinal cord will be performed the month preceding the procedure, after 1 year and thereafter with 2-yearly intervals. Sequences should include STIR or PD, T2, and T1 (with and without Gd) consistent with MAGNIMS recommendations [CITATION_1] .",
